collectors.title: Database
collectors.titleDetails: (2 total Queries, 2 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT hocsinh.MaHS, taikhoan.HoTen, taikhoan.NgaySinh FROM hocsinh JOIN taikhoan ON hocsinh.MaTK = taikhoan.MaTK LEFT JOIN hocsinh_lop ON hocsinh.MaHS = hocsinh_lop.MaHS AND hocsinh_lop.NamHoc = '2023-2024' WHERE hocsinh_lop.MaHS IS NULL AND hocsinh.MaHS NOT IN ( SELECT MaHS FROM hocsinh_lop WHERE NamHoc = CONCAT(SUBSTRING('2023-2024', 1, 4) - 1, '-', SUBSTRING('2023-2024', 6, 4) - 1) AND (MaLop = 5 OR MaLop = 6) )
